An autonomous sourcing future

Procurement teams use Fairmarkit’s autonomous sourcing platform to engage business users early, automate repetitive spend, and build a strategic sourcing process that delights stakeholders and delivers results. From nascent procurement functions at high-growth businesses, to established Fortune 50 enterprises, Fairmarkit is how it gets done.
Learn more

Unlock team bandwidth

Liberate your teams from repetitive, manual tasks such as gathering demand, creating sourcing events, analyzing supplier responses, reporting on progress, spreadsheet-heavy workflows, and so much more. Simply put, Fairmarkit automates the grunt work and implements AI in ways that help you do more with less.
See how

Enable frictionless sourcing

Engage business users the moment they realize a need for goods or services. Provide a delightful digital experience with lightning fast cycle times. Invite cross-functional collaborators for strategic events. Gain a seat at the strategic table by exceeding cost-savings or ESG & diversity goals. Fairmarkit amplifies procurement impact. At scale.
See how

Gain data visibility

Make proactive and data-driven decisions to optimize sourcing on a continuous basis. Embedded dashboards provide a holistic snapshot of team performance, event analytics, spend & savings by segment, supplier utilization, and more.
See how

Integrate seamlessly

Realize ROI in record time with a rapid implementation process that requires minimal IT resources. Fairmarkit is enterprise-ready with ISO 27001 and SOC2 certifications, and bi-directional integrations for SAP Ariba, S4Hana, Coupa, SAP ECC, Oracle and more.
See how
